DisableIncompatiblePackagesModal.description:
The following enabled packages are incompatible with this change:
{{packages, join(multiline: true)}}

You can either disable all incompatible packages now, or resolve each conflict manually later.

EnableOptionalDependencies.description:
{{packageName}} specifies the following optional dependencies:
{{dependencies, join(multiline: true)}}

Do you want to enable them?

InstallCompatibleVariantsModal.description:
The following enabled variants are incompatible with this change, but compatible variants can be installed:
{{variants, join(multiline: true)}}

You can either automatically install and switch to compatible variants now, or resolve each conflict manually later.

RemoveConflictingFilesModal.description:
The following external files are conflicting with this plugin:
{{files, join(multiline: true)}}

Do you want to remove these files? Backeups will be created in {{pluginsBackup}}.

ReplaceExternalPackagesModal.description:
The following external packages are incompatible with this change:
{{features, join(multiline: true)}}

If you wish to replace them, please remove all corresponding files from your Plugins folder before continuing. Otherwise, you can resolve each conflict manually later.
